ut weather, temperature, or forecasts for any location. NOT for: historical weather data, severe weather alerts, or detailed meteorological analysis. No API key needed.</description>\n    <location>~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/weather/SKILL.md</location>\n  </skill>\n  <skill>\n    <name>admin-web</name>\n    <description>Execute des taches administratives en ligne : actualisation France Travail, declarations CAF, consultation impots, telechargement d&apos;attestations. Toujours avec confirmation obligatoire avant soumission.</description>\n    <location>~/.openclaw/skills/admin-web/SKILL.md</location>\n  </skill>\n  <skill>\n    <name>analyze-link</name>\n    <description>Extrait le contenu d&apos;une URL (YouTube, GitHub, article web, PDF) et le retourne en markdown. Detecte automatiquement le type de lien et route vers le bon extracteur : yt-dlp+transcription pour YouTube, gh CLI pour GitHub, scrapling pour le web, document-tools pour les PDF.</description>\n    <location>~/.openclaw/skills/analyze-link/SKILL.md</location>\n  </skill>\n  <skill>\n    <name>candidature-web</name>\n    <description>Postule automatiquement a des offres d&apos;emploi en ligne. Recherche des offres, remplit les formulaires de candidature, upload le CV, et soumet apres confirmation explicite. Utilise Playwright pour les sites connus et browser-use (IA adaptative) pour les sites inconnus ou si Playwright echoue.</description>\n    <location>~/.openclaw/skills/candidature-web/SKILL.md</location>\n  </skill>\n  <skill>\n    <name>cascade-search</name>\n    <description>Recherche web adaptative avec routage intelligent. Choisit automatiquement la meilleure strategie : Playwright pour les sites connus, Tavily + DuckDuckGo en parallele pour emails/prix/contacts, browser-use pour les sites inconnus, enrichissement Perplexity si necessaire.</description>\n    <location>~/.openclaw/skills/cascade-search/SKILL.md</location>\n  </skill>\n  <skill>\n    <name>frontend-design-ultimate</name>\n    <description>Create distinctive, production-grade static sites with React, Tailwind CSS, and shadcn/ui — no mockups needed. Generates bold, memorable designs from plain text requirements with anti-AI-slop aesthetics, mobile-first responsive patterns, and single-file bundling. Use when building landing pages, marketing sites, portfolios, dashboards, or any static web UI. Supports both Vite (pure static) and Next.js (Vercel deploy) workflows.</description>\n    <location>~/.openclaw/skills/frontend-design-ultimate/SKILL.md</location>\n  </skill>\n  <skill>\n    <name>mining-crypto</name>\n    <description>Mining infrastructure management for CPU and GPU operations. Use when working with mining servers, monitoring hashrate, troubleshooting miners, managing Wake-on-LAN, or generating mining reports. Supports Monero (RandomX) CPU mining with c3pool and ZANO GPU mining with HeroMiners. Includes server inventory, SSH access procedures, miner restart workflows, automated monitoring scripts, and periodic health checks.</description>\n    <location>~/.openclaw/skills/mining-crypto/SKILL.md</location>\n  </skill>\n  <skill>\n    <name>nextcloud</name>\n    <description>Comprehensive Nextcloud integration with 16 modules (Notes, Tasks, Calendar, Files, Contacts, Mail, Bookmarks, Deck, Tables, Forms, Collectives, Photos, Passwords, Cospend, Groupfolders) via CalDAV, WebDAV, CardDAV, SMTP/IMAP, and REST APIs. Production-grade with multi-agent isolation, offline queue, conflict detection, auto-start systemd daemons, and 136 commands.</description>\n    <location>~/.openclaw/skills/nextcloud/SKILL.md</location>\n  </skill>\n  <skill>\n    <name>pdf</name>\n    <description>Comprehensive PDF manipulation toolkit for extracting text and tables, creating new PDFs, merging/splitting documents, and handling forms. When Claude needs to fill in a PDF form or programmatically process, generate, or analyze PDF documents at scale.</description>\n    <location>~/.openclaw/ski